{"tid":880222,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人有強迫症？","createTime":"2018-10-28T15:00:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T16:23:34.000Z","uid":138138,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"18571276816ed68dace04e38921c116a7ed98c79","tid":880222,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:00:17.000Z","msg":"見到蚊一定要打死佢先安樂<br />\n打唔死隻眼就會係咁跟住佢<br />\n<br />\n見到人地覆自己一定會覆番佢，就算無野講都是但打d野，唔想見到對話框個項係人地打既對話<br />\n<br />\n對於擺位有固定模式，如果畀人搞亂左就一定要擺番岩佢<br />\n<br />\n一卒眼就會係咁卒，就算唔痕都會繼續，直到feel到痛<br />\n<br />\n不停洗手，洗極都覺得唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n刷牙刷最少十分鐘，明明刷完又會忍唔住再刷<br />\n<br />\n諗到再講"},{"pid":"55df2f3adfdf1576b5251254fc53252e2a1f2a39","tid":880222,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"有咩impairment ?"},{"pid":"c8e525b9dd064acf915e3880de9a28ffcb0bae93","tid":880222,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:02:24.000Z","msg":"一定要見到藍tick<br />\n唔可以係人地對話最尾"},{"pid":"d4560cca9d97208bc1d3d1792c7cd6da0ae18c88","tid":880222,"uid":124256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:02:49.000Z","msg":"見到假膠就要扑柒佢"},{"pid":"6b766e4f65500332142ee3dddca038413661938b","tid":880222,"uid":165024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:05:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">check有冇鎖門</span>"},{"pid":"56d0d6b330bbe319c69e2b6a8aa5c350acde0810","tid":880222,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55df2f3adfdf1576b5251254fc53252e2a1f2a39","tid":880222,"uid":81575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:01:22.000Z","msg":"有咩impairment ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T15:06:32.000Z","msg":"做唔到個人心情就會極差，打唔死隻蚊個心會勁在意，個人會好燥<br />\n<br />\n如果見到人地覆左自己但唔得閒覆住，個人就會集中唔到，後尾發現熄左data/wifi睇唔到可以解決到少少個問題，起碼唔得閒個陣睇唔到有無人覆<br />\n<br />\n刷牙成日刷到流血個d唔講啦"},{"pid":"c90808b7271b3aace396aceb7063aaabec222f64","tid":880222,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0